<h2>HVAC Systems for Oakland</h2>
<p>Oakland's Mediterranean climate requires HVAC systems designed for moderate heating needs and efficient cooling during warm summer months. Heat pumps are particularly well-suited for this climate, providing both heating and cooling with SEER ratings of 16-20 for optimal efficiency. Given Oakland's mild winter temperatures rarely dropping below 40¬∞F, heat pumps can operate efficiently year-round without requiring backup heating systems.</p>

